latestPosts.caption:
You’ll find me at this speakeasy bar. You just won’t actually find me.

📍 @ochobandra 

Food:

chicken taco – 6/10 (flavour was strong)
crunchy avocado taco – 6/10

paneer taco – 7/10 (flavours were really good. that one surprised me)

prawn taco – 7/10 (crunchy prawn worked great in the taco)

tater tots – 8/10 (absolutely loved the garlic + cheese. went so well with the potato)

chicken popcorn – 9/10 (amazing flavour. perfectly fried. ranch was a bonus)

truffle mac & cheese – 8/10 (cheesy, truffley - never a bad idea. maybe too much cheese for more than a few bites)

rocky road campfire – 9/10 (marshmallows, cracker, chocolate, fudge, ice cream — insane combo)

Drinks:

watermelon mocktail – 7/10 (great flavours)

coconut pomegranate mocktail – 10/10 (never had a better mocktail. that was insane)

mojito – 8/10 (had a very cool slushy texture)

latestPosts.caption:
Not saying this is your next dinner spot… but yeah, it is. 

📍 @gigibombay in bandra. 

Here’s a review of the food:

Avocado prawn phyllo cups – 7/10 (melt in your mouth, prawn and avocado go really well together)
Caramel chicken – 9/10 (perfectly crispy and chewy and so flavorful)
Pesto pizza – 8/10 (I’ve said enough)
Dragon roll sushi – 8/10 (the textures and the flavor were great)
Tiramisu – 9/10 (love minimalist tiramisu — super dense)
Cocktails – 9/10 (the presentation was great, so was the taste and they customized it too)
